### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5550/api/v1
@churchId = {{onboard_church.response.body.data.churchId}}
@userId = user-uuid-here

### Onboard a new church (session cookie / Bearer required)
# @name onboard_church
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/church
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "church": {
    "name": "Global Victory Church",
    "slug": "global-victory",
    "logo": "https://example.com/logo.png",
    "denomination": "Non-denominational"
  },
  "branch": {
    "name": "Main HQ",
    "address": "123 Faith Lane",
    "email": "hq@globalvictory.org"
  }
}

### Get church details
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}

### List all branches
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/branches?limit=10&offset=0

### Get overview report
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/reports

### Get messagings
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/messagings
